msgid ""
"The Markdown Viewer KPart allows KParts-using software to display files in "
"Markdown format in a rendered view."
msgstr ""
"„Markdown Viewer KPart“ ļauj programmām, kas izmanto „KParts“, parādīt "
"„Markdown“ formāta datnes renderētā skatā."
